      <title>胡塞武装领导人誓言将对美国的任何军事袭击做出“重大”回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/houthi-leader-vows-big-response-to-any-us-military-assault</link>
      <description><![CDATA[也门胡塞武装领导人威胁称，如果美国及其盟友对其采取军事行动，他们将做出“重大”回应。该组织近两个月来一直在红海袭击船只。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/houthi-leader-vows-big-response-to-any-us-military-assault</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 16:00:58 GMT</pubDate>
